OL,3,C'We won't hear the bangs': Ukrainian
OL,4,Ccity moves schools into metro stations
OL,6,FStill, the fear of seemingly random
OL,7,FRussian strikes makes school too much
OL,8,Fof a risk, and none of the city's
OL,9,Fschools are still used for lessons as
OL,10,Fit's too dangerous.
OL,12,FThe city has looked underground, to
OL,13,Fthe metro and newly built bunker
OL,14,Fschools to protect children as they
OL,15,Flearn.
OL,17,F"Here we won't hear anything. We won't
OL,18,Fhear the bangs," five-year-old Elmira
OL,19,FDergousova told CNN from her classroom.
