OL,3,C'We won't hear the bangs': Ukrainian
OL,4,Ccity moves schools into metro stations
OL,6,FNestled in an old pedestrian tunnel, a
OL,7,Ffew feet under the tarmac of the road
OL,8,Fabove, the classrooms are cozy and
OL,9,Fcolourful.
OL,11,F"I love Ukraine because of nature,"
OL,12,FElmira continued.
OL,14,F"We have different creatures that are
OL,15,Fnot in other countries. And we were
OL,16,Fprobably attacked because of that."
OL,18,FElmira's father is fighting on the
OL,19,Ffront lines and she was a refugee in
OL,20,FPoland with her mother for a year.
