OL,3,C'We won't hear the bangs': Ukrainian
OL,4,Ccity moves schools into metro stations
OL,6,FIn Kharkiv, air raid sirens sound
OL,7,Fsometimes more than a dozen times a
OL,8,Fday, Elmira's mother Olena Dergousova
OL,9,Ftold CNN.
OL,11,FVirtually every house was hit in her
OL,12,Fneighbourhood in the opening months of
OL,13,Fthe 2022 invasion, she said.
OL,15,FGiven the limited space in the metro
OL,16,Fschool, Elmira is forced to study from
OL,17,Fhome every other day. She uses
OL,18,Fsoftware and tablets pioneered during
OL,19,Fthe Covid-19 pandemic.
