OL,3,C'We won't hear the bangs': Ukrainian
OL,4,Ccity moves schools into metro stations
OL,6,FNearly 2,200 children attend classes
OL,7,Fin the metro school's five sites in
OL,8,Fstations across Kharkiv, up from 1,000
OL,9,Fin September when they opened,
OL,10,Faccording to Kharkiv's city hall,
OL,11,Fsolely at their parents' request.
OL,13,FIn total, 106 classes of children
OL,14,Fthrough grades 1-11 rotate through the
OL,15,F19 metro classrooms.
OL,17,FThat's a fraction of the tens of
OL,18,Fthousands of school age children in
OL,19,Fthe city, according to the city's
OL,20,Fmayor.
