OL,3,C'We won't hear the bangs': Ukrainian
OL,4,Ccity moves schools into metro stations
OL,6,FBut studying underground means a
OL,7,Fschool day without disruption, safe
OL,8,Ffrom the bombs and the fear of the
OL,9,Fsirens.
OL,11,F"The kids are probably getting used to
OL,12,Fit by now," Elmira's teacher Olena
OL,13,FRudakova said.
OL,15,F"They get used to it somehow."
